Steps in the code:

Check to see if reshape2 is installed and loads it

Imports the data as long as the features.txt and the test/train folders are in the working directory

combines the data into a tidy format

Add variable names

Creates pared down dataset with only means and STDs

Creates a unique code for the subject/activity pair

Creates a new dataset where each record is the mean of each of the subject activity pair

Finally, labels the activity codes
